stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Session start

    Idle --> Capturing: speaking_start
    Capturing --> Capturing: onUserAudio (PCM chunks)
    Capturing --> SpeakingEndDelay: speaking_end
    Capturing --> Finalizing: stream_end (AfterSilence 700ms)
    Capturing --> Finalizing: max_duration (8s cap)
    Capturing --> Finalizing: near_silence_abort

    SpeakingEndDelay --> Capturing: speaking_start (user resumes)
    SpeakingEndDelay --> Finalizing: timer fires (220-800ms)

    Finalizing --> SilenceGate: PCM signal analysis
    SilenceGate --> Dropped: near-silent (RMS/peak below threshold)
    SilenceGate --> ASRBridge: real speech detected

    ASRBridge --> CoalesceWindow: transcript ready
    ASRBridge --> CoalesceWindow: ASR timeout fallback (700ms)

    CoalesceWindow --> Dispatched: timer fires (1100ms, no follow-up)
    CoalesceWindow --> CoalesceWindow: new turn arrives → merge + reset timer
    CoalesceWindow --> Dispatched: follow-up arrives → merge + dispatch immediately

    Dispatched --> ReplyDecision: evaluateVoiceReplyDecision()
    ReplyDecision --> BotSpeaking: allow=true → response.create
    ReplyDecision --> Deferred: allow=false, reason=bot_turn_open
    ReplyDecision --> Idle: allow=false (skip)

    Deferred --> ReplyDecision: flush timer (1320ms) + re-evaluate
    BotSpeaking --> Idle: response_done + silence timeout

    Dropped --> Idle
